# Optional — only if you use Docker Compose for Postgres (see docs/local-development.md).
# Copy to `.env` in repo root. If you use a dedicated role/database on an existing Postgres
# server instead, you do not need this file.
#
# `npm run db:up` fails with "address already in use" on 5432: set a free host port and
# match it in `backend/.env` → DATABASE_URL.
#
# FINBAR_PG_PUBLISH_PORT=5433
